Title: oracle_recovery_status: backupcheck for user managed backups
Level: 1
Component: checks
Compatible: compat
Version: 1.2.7i1
Date: 1420969906
Class: feature

A new check for manual backups has been added. The check monitors the
backup state for all datafiles when using the manual backup mode. This
has no function when RMAN is used for backing up an Oracle Database!
